OL,3,C'The report is a horror show' -
OL,4,CFamilies of victims killed in
OL,5,CNottingham react
OL,7,FThe families of Barnaby Webber, Grace
OL,8,FO' Malley Kumar and Ian Coates have
OL,9,Freemphasised their call for a new
OL,10,Fpublic inquiry.
OL,12,FValdo Calocane, who had been diagnosed
OL,13,Fwith paranoid schizophrenia, was
OL,14,Fsentenced to an indefinite hospital
OL,15,Forder after killing 19-year-old
OL,16,Fstudents Barnaby Webber, Grace
OL,17,FO'Malley-Kumar and 65-year-old
OL,18,Fcaretaker Ian Coates in June 2023.
