OL,3,C'The report is a horror show' -
OL,4,CFamilies of victims killed in
OL,5,CNottingham react
OL,7,FThe knifeman also attempted to kill
OL,8,Fthree other people in the spate of
OL,9,Fattacks in Nottingham.
OL,11,FThe families of the victims have been
OL,12,Fspeaking at a press conference in
OL,13,FLondon in reaction to the NHS
OL,14,FNottinghamshire healthcare's report
OL,15,Fwhich details the contact Calocane had
OL,16,Fwith mental health services.
OL,18,FEmma Webber, the mother of Barnaby
OL,19,Fsaid it was "unfathomable" that the
OL,20,Ffamilies have had to fight for lessons
OL,21,Fto be learned.
