OL,3,C'The report is a horror show' -
OL,4,CFamilies of victims killed in
OL,5,CNottingham react
OL,7,F"The scale of this is unimaginable and
OL,8,Fof an epic level.
OL,10,F"It must be addressed. No more empty
OL,11,Fpromises. Anything that could go
OL,12,Fwrong, did and it is for a public
OL,13,Finquiry to take this forward.
OL,15,F"To the prime minister and rest of the
OL,16,Fgovernment, make this trauma stop, and
OL,17,Fmake our fight stop now."
