OL,5,CNottingham react
OL,7,FShe called on the government to "do
OL,8,Fthe right thing" make the public
OL,9,Finquiry statutory and said "we won't
OL,10,Fstop until that happens".
OL,12,FMs Webber said: "I am certain our
OL,13,Fstory, our tragedy and this
OL,14,Fdisgraceful miscarriage of justice...
OL,15,Fwould have been brushed under the
OL,16,Fcarpet".
OL,18,FSolicitor Neil Hudgell said the
OL,19,Ffamilies would meet the government
OL,20,Fnext week to discuss a statutory
OL,21,Fpublic inquiry.
