OL,7,FIn reaction, Dr Sanjoy Kumar, the
OL,8,Ffather of Grace said the "report falls
OL,9,Fshort as a doctor and I am thoroughly
OL,10,Fdisgusted".
OL,12,FHe says he would like to see
OL,13,Findividuals to be named and echoed the
OL,14,Ffamilies views that '"we demand
OL,15,Faccountability.
OL,17,F"He was sectioned four times.
OL,19,F"Four times the psychiatrists failed
OL,20,Fto change the treatment.
