OL,7,F"Four times they failed to put
OL,8,Fprovisions to ensure he took his
OL,9,Fmedication, ultimately discharging him
OL,10,Finto the community to do harm."
OL,12,FMs Webber said: "This report is a
OL,13,Fhorror show, it uncovers failings on
OL,14,Fan epic level".
