OL,3,C'The report is a horror show' -
OL,4,CFamilies of victims killed in
OL,5,CNottingham react
OL,7,FJames Coates, the son of Ian Coates
OL,8,Fsaid: "My dad had grandchildren who
OL,9,Fwould be going to school and college
OL,10,Fin the next few years and to think the
OL,11,Fsame thing could happen to them as
OL,12,Fwhat happened to Barnaby and Grace is
OL,13,Fheartbreaking".
OL,15,FHe said he cannot have "faith in the
OL,16,Ftrust because they won't pick out the
OL,17,Findividuals and the one who signed on
OL,18,Fthe dotted line and let that murderer
OL,19,Fcome out and kill my father and kill
OL,20,Ftwo students".
