OL,7,FThe review said other patients cared
OL,8,Ffor by Nottinghamshire Healthcare NHS
OL,9,FFoundation Trust also committed
OL,10,F"extremely serious" acts of violence `
OL,11,Fincluding stabbings ` between 2019 and
OL,12,F2023.
OL,14,FThe NHS took the decision to publish
OL,15,Fthe report in full after originally
OL,16,Fsaying that only a redacted version
OL,17,Fwould be released because of
OL,18,F"protection legislation relating to
OL,19,Fpatient information".
